<h4 class="ez_pagetitle">PHP/MySQL</h4>
<div id="ez_msg">
<div id="ez_header">
<span class="ez_label">From:</span> Bill Morris &lt;bill.boykinmorris@...&gt;<br />
<span class="ez_label">Date:</span> Mon, 16 Jul 2012 11:58:14 -0400<br />
